R‑002 Model mismatch (unmodelled dynamics) SCBF forward invariance Dynamics correctly modelled Assumption must be validated externally
R‑003 Plan execution error Dependent type ensures action correctness Proof assistant sound Trust in proof assistant kernel
R‑004 Composition of certificates breaks safety Homotopy equivalence preserves safety Univalence axiom holds Axiom accepted in type theory
R‑005 Sensor failure not captured by model Not covered by current proofs — Accepted limitation

All assumptions are explicitly stated in the mathematical model; no empirical validation is required for the theoretical framework.

